<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Transaction Notification - <%= siteName %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #dc2626);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .transaction-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .transaction-field {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .transaction-field:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .field-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .field-value {
            color: #111827;
        }
        .status-success {
            color: #10b981;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .status-pending {
            color: #f59e0b;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .status-failed {
            color: #dc2626;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #1f2937;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .security-notice h3 {
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Transaction <%= status.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + status.slice(1) %></h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= userName %>,</p>
            
            <p>Your transaction has been <span class="status-<%= status %>"><%= status %></span>.</p>
            
            <div class="transaction-details">
                <div class="transaction-field">
                    <span class="field-label">Transaction ID:</span>
                    <span class="field-value"><%= transactionId %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="transaction-field">
                    <span class="field-label">Type:</span>
                    <span class="field-value"><%= type %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="transaction-field">
                    <span class="field-label">Amount:</span>
                    <span class="amount"><%= amount %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="transaction-field">
                    <span class="field-label">From:</span>
                    <span class="field-value"><%= fromCurrency %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="transaction-field">
                    <span class="field-label">To:</span>
                    <span class="field-value"><%= toCurrency %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="transaction-field">
                    <span class="field-label">Exchange Rate:</span>
                    <span class="field-value"><%= exchangeRate %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="transaction-field">
                    <span class="field-label">Fee:</span>
                    <span class="field-value"><%= fee %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="transaction-field">
                    <span class="field-label">Status:</span>
                    <span class="status-<%= status %>"><%= status.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + status.slice(1) %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="transaction-field">
                    <span class="field-label">Date:</span>
                    <span class="field-value"><%= new Date().toLocaleString() %></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <% if (status === 'completed') { %>
                <p>‚úÖ Your transaction has been completed successfully! The funds have been processed and should be available in your account.</p>
            <% } else if (status === 'pending') { %>
                <p>‚è≥ Your transaction is being processed. You will receive another notification once it&apos;s completed.</p>
            <% } else if (status === 'failed') { %>
                <p>‚ùå Your transaction could not be completed. Please contact our support team for assistance.</p>
            <% } %>
            
            <div class="security-notice">
                <h3>üîí Security Notice</h3>
                <p>If you didn&apos;t initiate this transaction, please contact our support team immediately at <strong>support@apicts.com</strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <p>You can view all your transactions in your account dashboard.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The APICTS Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> APICTS. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated transaction notification. Please keep this email for your records.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

